Package org.kuali.kfs.module.ld.document.web.struts

Interface Summary
MultipleValueLookupBroker Interface for defining a ActionForm that has multiple value lookups on it; however, it should not be implemented by a class that extends LookupForm or MultipleValueLookupForm unless you have a really, really good reason.
